# API Documentation

This documentation provides details about the available routes and their corresponding functionalities for the API.

## Users

### Register User

Registers a new user.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/register`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 201

### Login User

Logs in an existing user.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/login`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 201

### Get All Users

Retrieves all users.

- Method: GET
- Endpoint: `/api/users`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 200

### Get Friends of a User

Retrieves all friends of a particular user identified by their ID.

- Method: GET
- Endpoint: `/api/users/:id/friends`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 200

### Send Friend Request

Sends a friend request to another user identified by their ID.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/users/:id/friends`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 201

### Accept/Reject Friend Request

Accepts or rejects a friend request.

- Method: PATCH
- Endpoint: `/api/users/:id/friends/:friendId`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 204

## Posts

### Create a Post

Creates a new post.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/posts`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 201

### Get All Posts

Retrieves all posts.

- Method: GET
- Endpoint: `/api/posts`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 200

### Get Post by ID

Retrieves a specific post by its ID.

- Method: GET
- Endpoint: `/api/posts/:id`
- Authentication: No
- Status Code: 200

### Update Post by ID

Updates a specific post by its ID.

- Method: PATCH
- Endpoint: `/api/posts/:id`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 204

### Delete Post by ID

Deletes a specific post by its ID.

- Method: DELETE
- Endpoint: `/api/posts/:id`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 202

### Like a Post

Likes a specific post.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/posts/:id/likes`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 201

### Comment on a Post

Adds a comment to a specific post.

- Method: POST
- Endpoint: `/api/posts/:id/comments`
- Authentication: Yes
- Status Code: 201
